<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> مَنَاقِبِ عُثْمَانَ بْنِ عَفَّانَ، أَبِي عَمْرٍو، الْقُرَشِيِّ <span class="special">﵁</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(مَنْ يَحْفِرْ بِئْرَ رُومَةَ فَلَهُ الْجَنَّةُ)</span>. فَحَفَرَهَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عُثْمَانُ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(مَنْ جَهَّزَ جَيْشَ الْعُسْرَةِ فَلَهُ الْجَنَّةُ)</span>. فَجَهَّزَهُ عُثْمَانُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٢٦٢٦]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>